  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">PF 12-637 Improved Livelihoods Cocoa Samoa (A13123)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">A previous Partnerships-funded Activity, the Samoa Cocoa Export Improvement Programme, identified opportunities in enabling resilience and developing optimal cocoa returns. It is proposed that MFAT coinvest with SPS Biosecurity to develop&#xA0;two Value Chains, with&#xA0;a primary focus on sustaining the production of premium cocoa, and a secondary focus on promoting Samoa&#xA0;in agritourism. The Activity will include a training component, which will see rural youth trained in agribusiness skills.</narrative>
  </description>
